<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Jury President Cate Blanchett joined fellow member Matt Dillon at the socially distanced 77th Venice Film Festival on Wednesday. </p>

<p>The 51-year-old looked incredible wearing a striped jumpsuit which she cinched in at the waist wearing a contrasting thick red belt. </p>

<p> Arriving wearing a face mask, she removed it for photos, keeping her distance from Matt for safety purposes amid the Covid: 19 pandemic. </p>

<p>A-list: Jury President Cate Blanchett (left) joined fellow member Matt Dillon (right) at the socially distanced 77th Venice Film Festival on Wednesday</p>

<p>Safety first: The pair arrived at their photocall wearing face masks and kept a little apart due to the Covid: 19 pandemic </p>

<p>Matt, 56, kept things simple in a dark blue suit which he dressed down with a plain matching jumper as he posed for photos. </p>

<p>According to Variety, when the Film Festival unveiled its official selection in late July, the 'unprecedented inclusion of eight female-directed titles within the 18-film roster was heralded as welcome progress for an event that has come under fire in recent years for scarce representation of female filmmakers.'</p>

<p>Cate was chosen to head the jury back in January, making her the third woman in four years to hold the role. </p>

<p>Wow! Cate cut a striking figure in her striped jumpsuit, wearing a contrasting red belt to cinch herself in at the waist </p>

<p>Important role: Cate was chosen to head the jury back in January, making her the third woman in four years to hold the role</p>

<p>Replacement: Matt is stepping in for Cristi Puiu as a member on the competition jury after the Romanian director had to pull out of the event</p>

<p>On her way: When the Film Festival unveiled its official selection in late July, the ' unprecedented inclusion of eight female-directed titles within the 18-film roster was heralded as welcome progress'</p>

<p>Matt is stepping in for Cristi Puiu as a member on the competition jury after the Romanian director had to pull out of the event.</p>

<p>Earlier on in the day, Victoria's Secret model Taylor Hill, 24, put on a stylish display upon her arrival, looking sensational in a denim jumpsuit that had a clashing print and puffy sleeves.</p>

<p>Taylor's ensemble also featured a chic ruffled neckline that had a paisley print, while she cinched her outfit at the waist with a statement black belt.</p>

<p>Easy disguise: Matt was difficult to spot as he made his way inside the Excelsior venue </p>

<p>So glam: Cate looked incredible even wearing her mask as she posed for some snaps </p>

<p>All stars: (L-R) Venezia77 Jury Members Nicola Lagioia, Joanna Hogg, Veronika Franz, Venezia77 Jury President Cate , Matt , Ludivine Sagnier and Christian Petzold</p>

<p>She stepped out in a pair of black strap sandals, and colour-coordinated the look by keeping her personal items in a small handbag. </p>

<p>The model's cropped brunette locks were brushed into loose waves that framed her face well, and she used a light palette of make-up for the outing.</p>

<p>After stepping off her boat onto the jetty and posing for snaps, Taylor was seen putting on a blue face mask to keep safe during the COVID-19 pandemic. </p>

<p>The Venice Film Festival is one of the world's oldest award ceremonies and is listed as one of the 'Big Five' events. It starts on 2 September and ends on the 12 September. </p>

<p>Though the event is still taking place, it is a markedly toned down affair to previous years amid the coronavirus crisis, with temperature checks and mask wearing becoming mandatory. </p>

